[On top of the above-mentioned 1st outbreak in Normandy, another focus of
infection (or suspected infection? serological?) has been discovered,
namely in Elstead. The current infected zone includes areas around 3
locations: Pirbright, Normandy, and Elstead. See further updated details in
item [3] below, and a current map of the protection and surveillance zones
at
<http://www.defra.gov.uk/footandmouth/pdf/declaration-pz-sz-rz-070805.pdf>.
